Use Specific Commans by L2Minius
.cfg OR .control = Control Pannel
.getreward = Vote Commands
.combine OR .talisman = Combine Talismans
.stream = Streaming Command
.repair = Repair your Character
.offline = Set your Offline Store
.buffstore = Set your Buff Store
.buffshield = Protects your Buffs
.siege = Register in Siege & Fortress
.dressme = Dress your Gear
.npcspawn = ClanLeader spawn NPCS in ClanHall
.party (message) = Find Party System
CTRL + Left Mouse Click = For Atry Stones and MP/HP/CP Potion Auto Mode
